 grains, or steam for 8 hours.&amp;nbsp; Peroxide isn't going to cut it for grains.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;For the record, any more talk of dealing in this thread is going to result in some ban points handed out. . .&lt;br /&gt;RR</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>18574129</next>\n<prev>18573996</prev>\n<first>18572827</first>\n<last>18609378</last>\n<when>1374126913</when>\n<utime>07/18/13 08:55 AM</utime>\n</post>"}